  "detailed_description": "<strong>Drill, craft, upgrade and explore in MIneDrill Redux!</strong><br><br>After a disastrous rocket crash, drill down the earth to find ores that will help you rebuild your rocket and fly back home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>12 types of ores to mine<br></li><li>Crafting system<br></li><li>Randomly generated worlds<br></li><li>Drill upgrades based on items<br></li><li>Enemies<br></li><li>Treasures and caves</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coming Soon:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Improved graphics and sounds<br></li><li>More enemies and a better combat system<br></li><li>Steam achievements<br></li><li>A nice story</li></ul>",
